  <md:title>Friction</md:title>
  <md:abstract><list id="list-00001">
<item>Discuss the general characteristics of friction.</item>
<item>Describe the various types of friction.</item>
<item>Calculate the magnitude of static and kinetic friction.</item>
</list></md:abstract>
